---
const stats = [
  { value: "24/7", label: "Transfer availability planning" },
  { value: "3", label: "Premium fleet categories" },
  { value: "1", label: "WhatsApp-first booking flow" },
];
---

<section class="container-page section-padding">
  <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-stretch">
    <div class="luxury-surface rounded-[8px] p-6 sm:p-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#e2e8f0]/60">Private travel standard</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[#e2e8f0] sm:text-4xl">
        Designed for guests who want the route handled before they arrive.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400 sm:text-base">
        STEP 2 completes the homepage content foundation with sharper positioning for airport transfer,
        private island tour, VIP driver movement, and flexible concierge-style travel.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
        {stats.map((item) => (
          <div class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#e2e8f0]">{item.value}</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500">{item.label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative min-h-80 overflow-hidden rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#111827] p-6 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(0,0,0,0.28)] sm:p-8">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 visual-placeholder opacity-80"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(130deg,rgba(11,12,16,0.34),rgba(11,12,16,0.9)_72%)]"></div>
      <div class="relative flex h-full min-h-64 flex-col justify-end">
        <span class="w-fit rounded-full border border-white/14 bg-black/24 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#e2e8f0]/80">
          Eco-luxury inspired
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[#e2e8f0] sm:text-3xl">
          Calm cabin mood, private timing, and island-aware route decisions.
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">
          The homepage now has enough visual and content structure to guide visitors from desire,
          to service choice, to WhatsApp availability without feeling like a generic travel template.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
